org.omnaest.utils.table
Interface Stripe<E>

Type Parameters:
E -
All Superinterfaces:
ImmutableStripe<E>, Iterable<E>, Serializable
All Known Subinterfaces:
Column<E>, Row<E>
public interface Stripe<E>
extends ImmutableStripe<E>

Base type of Row and Column.

The ImmutableStripe.to() method allows to transform the content of the given Stripe into other forms like List, Set, Map, etc.

Author:
Omnaest
See Also:
StripeTransformer, ImmutableStripe, Table
